Asia-Pacific is projected to witness the fastest growth during the forecast period, fueled by rising diabetes prevalence, increasing healthcare investments, expanding middle-class populations, and government initiatives promoting digital healthcare solutions.
Meanwhile, South America and the Middle East & Africa continue to present attractive long-term opportunities as healthcare accessibility and awareness continue to improve.
